[For clarification, because the statement is not accurate, Goias is
not on the Bolivian border. Those that are, from north to south,
include Acre, Rondonia, Mato Grosso, and Mato Grosso do Sul. - Mod.LJS]

[The dengue virus serotype that is reported to be recently detected
in Bolivia is not specified in this report, but dengue virus type 2
was reported as having been recently detected in the report from
Bolivia, above.

